ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of KAREN JUNE HILL of Ohsweken, Ontario, to be a director of the board of directors of The Federal Bridge Corporation Limited, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective February 1, 2019, in the place of Gary Laverne Atkinson, whose term will expire.
